data.description: This beautiful home is located on a quiet street and has had many updates. The upper levels feature a living room, formal and informal dining areas, a mudroom and a spacious, bright kitchen with new stainless-steel appliances. The upper level also offer 3 bedrooms on 1 level. The roomy primary bedroom suite features a private 3/4 bathroom and walk in closet. The lower-level family room features beautiful built in cabinets, fireplace and opens to a large stamped concrete patio and a gorgeous, private backyard. The lower level bathroom is beautifully remodeled with a quartz countertop. 4th level is finished with a large recreation room that features new carpet and large storage area. Home is conveniently situated in a south metro suburb near parks, shopping, highways, businesses, schools & recreation areas.
